E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Art Class: When Tina and Gemma get more than they bargained for in a revealing art class, Calvin gets jealous and takes drastic action. (S3 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Valentino Submergence: Sheldon and Amy host a special live Valentine's Day episode of their internet show Fun with Flags. Leonard and Penny grapple with getting older. (S9 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Positive Negative Reaction: When Bernadette makes a big announcement, Howard becomes convinced that he needs to start earning more money. (S9 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Financial Permeability: When Sheldon lends Penny some money, it brings her ex-boyfriend Kurt back into her life, with negative consequences for the gang. (S2 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks Omnibus
E4Plus1.uk.description: Dillon opens up to Frankie, but a shocking proposal leaves him stunned. Darren continues to protest his innocence, Cleo struggles to adapt to motherhood, and Warren offers Mercedes support.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip from Rude Tube's naughty little sister that features a variety of cats doing strange things, some soldiers stuck in the sand and a dog balancing on a rope.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Come Dine with Me: Teens
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: In this youthful mouthful, five teenagers compete to win ¬£1000. Aminah rolls out the red carpet for an Oscar-themed evening. Can she deliver a winning performance? (Ep1/5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Come Dine with Me: Teens
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Ben hopes that his menu of family faves will impress, as long as he figures out how to work the oven! After a slow start, can he salvage his night and bag the win? (Ep2/5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Come Dine with Me: Teens
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Letty treats her guests to a night of Italian feasting. Can she deliver a slice of la dolce vita, or will her cake be more of a red flag than the Italian flag? (Ep3/5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Come Dine with Me: Teens
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Beatle-maniac Zach hosts a music-inspired night. But when a guest launches a fork at the table, can Zach compose himself and serve up a musical masterpiece? (Ep4/5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Come Dine with Me: Teens
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Alex goes all-out by making absolutely everything from scratch. Will the fruits of his labour pay off with his dessert, or will he crumble under the pressure? (Ep5/5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: It's the final boys' and girls' nights out, with old friends joining in the fun. But one familiar face's shocking revelation sparks the mother of all showdowns. (S10 Ep31)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: At the final dinner party, celebrations and deliberations are served, with a side of double standards. And one couple question whether their love can survive. (S10 Ep32)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: It's vow renewal time! As the couples return home to prepare for the big decision, one couple leave on bad terms and a bride questions her husband's feelings. (S10 Ep33)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: It's commitment crunch time as the vow renewals continue. One emotional groom questions whether he's enough, and a couple decide whether long-distance can work. (S10 Ep34)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK: Reunion
E4Plus1.uk.description: Reunion: Brand new series - It's the reunion dinner party and in true MAFS style, across-the-table action is served as two brides clash. And one groom faces a reckoning! (S10 Ep35)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK: Reunion
E4Plus1.uk.description: Reunion: Brand new series - In the reunion Commitment Ceremony, some couples celebrate their journeys, others confront their issues, and one final admission rocks the group. (S10 Ep36)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Celebration Experimentation: The gang persuade Sheldon to celebrate his birthday and invite a few special guests along to his party, in the 200th episode. (S9 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Application Deterioration: Leonard, Sheldon and Howard run into problems when they file for a patent. Emily reaches out to Raj after their break-up. (S9 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Great New Year Bake Off
E4Plus1.uk.description: Another chance to see familiar faces Maxy, J√ºrgen, Maggie and Mark compete to win the first Star Baker of 2024, before they see the New Year in with a performance from Bone-Afide.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Peeping Mom: Bart lies to cover up his role in a bulldozer crash, so Marge decides to follow him everywhere until he confesses. Ned's cute new dog loves Homer. (S26 Ep18/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Kids Are All Fight: When Homer finds an old roll of film and has it developed, the family take a trip down memory lane to when Bart and Lisa were always fighting. (S26 Ep19/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Mission: Impossible - Ghost...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...Protocol: (2011) Part four of the Tom Cruise action-thriller franchise. The Impossible Missions Force fight to clear their name, while also trying to avert nuclear war. Busy, busy, busy!
